{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_11_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 道を切り開いてみせます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影終了から数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after the MV shoot finished",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6665037,
          "startTime": 1.5666665037
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、愛？　こんな所でどうした\n今日は現場から直接寮に帰るんじゃなかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ Ai? What are you doing here?\nWeren’t you supposed to go straight back to the dorm from the set today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7752150179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、お疲れ様です、{user}さん！\n今日、MVの完成映像が届くって聞いて待ちきれなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ good work today‚ {user}-san!\nI heard the completed MV was arriving today‚ and I just couldn’t wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8133780163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.0467121125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "すぐに観たくて、アポなしで事務所まで来ちゃいました\n……けどすみません、お忙しかったですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I came to the office without an appointment to watch it right away.\n…But‚ sorry‚ were you busy…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0467121125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "よく考えたら、なんだか申し訳なくなってきました……\nすみません、出直してきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that I think about it‚ I feel kind of bad…\nI’m sorry‚ I’ll come back later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7467121125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.0343086204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺は大丈夫だから一緒に確認しよう\n全力で取り組んだ成果だ、気になるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s fine. Let’s check it together.\nIt’s the result of all our hard work. I want to see it too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.8200682284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます～！\nそれじゃ、ぜひご一緒させて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much~!\nThen‚ please let me watch it together with you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1039678892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.093652944
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.343652944
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ところで愛……なんでMV撮影の衣装に着替えたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Ai… why did you change into your MV outfit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.143652944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "だって{user}さん、MV撮影の日は\n前の仕事が押して、撮影に立ち会えませんでしたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ {user}-san‚ on the day of the MV shoot‚\nyour previous work ran late and you couldn’t attend the shoot‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3753980956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.4535394314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくですし、映像越しじゃなくて\n直に披露したいなって思って。どうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I thought‚ not just through the video‚\nI wanted to present it in person. What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8753980956,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13304.211642100008,
          "startTime": 77.1796097377
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 67.8859837338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、これを着てるとMV撮影時の気持ちを\n新鮮に思い返せる気がして。それじゃ、再生しますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ wearing this makes me feel the emotions\nfrom the MV shoot fresh again. Well then‚ I’ll play it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3029438339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今回のMVは、いろいろな場所で撮影したんだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This MV was shot in various locations‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5831267481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.7015004918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　あの日最高のステージになったのは\nみんなが自由と楽しさを思い出せたからだと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I believe what made that day our best stage\nwas that everyone remembered freedom and fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0394807182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.1015006189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、それぞれの思い入れがある場所や\n好きな場所で、肩の力を抜いて四人で踊ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So at each place that had special meaning‚\nthe four of us relaxed and danced in our favorite spots.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.088435576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.1408670232
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.1408670232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "最初は……\nNEXT VENUSグランプリの会場だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First…\nThis is the venue for the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4333367031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4884343908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "ここは、LizNoirにとって、全員の\n思い入れがある場所ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This place holds meaning for\neveryone in LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.022650274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.426915213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵さん、お二人の覚悟と想いを\n私とこころが身をもって感じた場所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The determination and feelings of Rio-san and Aoi-san\nare something Kokoro and I experienced firsthand here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3893169407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "……凄く申し訳ない想いもあるけれど\n今のLizNoirになった、きっかけの場所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I also feel very apologetic‚ but\nthis is the place that led to the LizNoir we are now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8893169407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.4988430149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "最初はやっぱりここじゃないとね、って\n莉央さんが選んだ場所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san chose this place‚ saying‚\n“If we’re starting somewhere‚ it has to be here.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.222650274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.2246710903
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.2246710903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そして次は……星見市の、海の近くか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And next… near the sea in Hoshimi City‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2746710903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.0852130698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "こころの案です！　星見市も、星見プロも\n今やLizNoirにとって大事な場所ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was Kokoro’s idea! Hoshimi City and Hoshimi Pro\nare now important places for LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.071355375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-night",
      "startTime": 144.2451175815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロに移籍してからの私達は\n本当の意味で、四人体制になっていきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After transferring to Hoshimi Pro‚ we\ntruly became a four-member unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1380403523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "星見市で行った事務所総出のスペシャルライブも\n四人になったリズノワのライブも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The special live held by the entire agency in Hoshimi City‚\nthe LizNoir live after we became a four-member group‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9713736856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
